snippet.title: BIG Changes to New World with the 1.2 Winter Update...
snippet.description:
In New World's December 1.2 Update we're getting a New Winter/Christmas event, new Ice Cave Dungeons, the new "expertise" system and more!
Check out the full patch notes (so far) here: https://www.newworld.com/en-gb/news/articles/december-ptr-announcement

Tune into the stream and watch Baggins live Monday to Saturday at: https://www.twitch.tv/bagginstv

Join the Company Discord to continue the conversation about all things New World: https://discord.gg/fFQut5MuK7

00:00 Intro
01:20 General Changes
07:04 Crafting Changes
08:47 Winter Event Stuff
15:51 New Anti-Healing Perks
17:48 New Gypsum/Expertise System
